				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Trung-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/C%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i-thi/poem-0KVjKnYZtlXpzry27CYrVw">Cảm hoài thi - 感懷詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Trung-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-vwkwYNzCnKHaayHMN3KvlQ">Viên Trung Đạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/C%E1%BB%95-h%E1%BB%8Dc-vi%E1%BB%87n-h%C3%A0n-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-ng%E1%BA%ABu-ng%C3%A2m/poem--38dpEvu7fH2Mvb9y8ZERw">Cổ học viện hàn đông ngẫu ngâm - 古學院冬寒偶吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-Khu%C3%B4ng/Cung-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%A9-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0u-C%E1%BA%A7u-An-Nam-ch%C6%B0-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BA%A7n-thi/poem-2VUK_nUH_igs10W7XnLMtQ">Cung hoạ ngự chế tứ Triều Tiên, Lưu Cầu, An Nam chư quốc sứ thần thi - 恭和御制賜朝鮮琉球安南諸國使臣詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-Khu%C3%B4ng/author-mkalWlWp8YHB5cBK0ePleg">Nguyễn Hoằng Khuông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Qu%C3%BD-T%E1%BB%B5-thu-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-th%C4%83ng-S%C6%A1n-Nam-x%E1%BB%A9-T%E1%BA%A3-m%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%91%C4%83ng-tr%C3%ACnh-ng%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc/poem-5YnPZj1DPRNHxnrISZqDWg">Quý Tỵ thu phụng thăng Sơn Nam xứ Tả mạc đăng trình ngẫu đắc - 癸巳秋奉陞山南處左瘼登程偶得</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Th%E1%BA%A5m-vi%C3%AAn-xu%C3%A2n/poem-_ZbPgmSzdWi_I8yN-bb3zQ">Thấm viên xuân - 沁園春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C